  "name": "Mounted Praetor",
  "titles": "Mounted Praetor",
  "lore": "When additional mobility is required, Praetors will often opt to ride to war astride a Scimitar jetbike or Spatha bike. Providing unparalleled speed and additional firepower, these powerful mounts allow a Praetor to swiftly respond to threats across the battlefront, bringing their skill and expertise to bear wherever it is required. While limiting the wargear they can bring to battle, the ability to approach the enemy at speed like the cavalry of antiquity more than compensates, and the most skilled riders can bring their heavy weaponry to bear as they close with the foe before riding down the survivors with their blade.",
